Extract Table example#

[1]:

from target_annotation import ExtractTable

Use results from TargetAnnotation module#

[2]:

annotate_db_file = "~/results/target_annotation.json"

Setup class#

[3]:

pipe = ExtractTable(
    annotate_db=annotate_db_file,
    output_path="~/results",
)

Get table and key#

[4]:

res, res_key = pipe.get_table()
